data.description: Come check out this charming home nestled in a quiet neighborhood! You are welcomed into this home with a spacious open floor plan and soaring ceilings. The kitchen includes ample counter, storage space and an island for an additional place to prepare meals. Easy connection to the kitchen and family room make entertaining and socializing a breeze. The spacious primary includes its own en suite and sizable closet. You will truly enjoy the Texas weather with this covered patio and sizable yard complete with a privacy fence and mature trees. Don't miss the chance to own this wonderful home located within minutes to I-35, New Braunfels and local entertainment. This convenient location will truly allow you to enjoy some of the major attractions and establishments San Antonio and New Braunfels have to offer! Schedule a showing today!
